# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added

- `cmd/mylittlepoller-winsvc` application binary package that will be run as a Windows service. This is explained in README.
- `web` package containing `mlp-frontend` Vue project as a subproject. `web` implements server functionality and when used in an executable, will serve the `mlp-frontend` Vue frontend project.  
- LICENSE, README and CHANGELOG files.

[Unreleased]: https://github.com/Trashed/mylittlepoller